                        <div class="container">
                            <p>
                                Shipping of the order from we are very safe, secure and hassle free. All our 
                                products are insured during the in transit by “The New India Assurance Co.”</p>
                            <p>
                                Every package of product (Jewellery / Gold Coin) purchased from we will reach to 
                                your doorstep in a durable condition and in a tamper-proof packing. Our courier 
                                partners are Bluedart, Ecom Express, Malca Amit and BVC. We dispatch through any 
                                of the courier partner depending upon their serviceability in the shipping 
                                address.</p>
                            <p>
                                <b>Shipping Charges:</b></p>
                            <p>
                                Shipping is FREE OF COST across all over India. In the recent update from some 
                                of the state governments Entry Tax is applicable on 
                                Jewellery/Coin/Solitaire/Watches purchase which is to be paid by customer at the 
                                time of entry of the product into their state. To make this process simple our 
                                courier team will make the payment on behalf of customer and we shall be 
                                collecting the same from you after placing the order by sending manual payment 
                                link. At present the states which have entry taxes are listed below:</p>
                            <br />
                            <p>
                                <b>Delivery to Identified Person</b></p>
                            <p>
                                Customer have to enter the correct details of Consignee / Recipient Name (as it 
                                is stated in their photo identification that is approved by the Government) with 
                                complete Address, nearby landmark, pin code and contact number for hassle free 
                                delivery.<br />
                                As the product reaches the destination, at the time of delivery, the recipient 
                                will have to provide any of the mentioned below identity proofs to collect the 
                                product:<br />
                                <br />
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Passport</li>
                                <li>PAN Card</li>
                                <li>Drivers License</li>
                                <li>Voters ID</li>
                                <li>Ration Card</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>
                                <br />
                                We make sure that delivery is made with the help of courier agent after checking 
                                the identity proof of the recipient and the courier agent confirms the same. To 
                                make sure that the delivery is safe and secured, the courier agent will note 
                                down details of the recipient&#39;s identity proof. During this process, the 
                                receiver is expected to cooperate with the agent by providing with original 
                                copies of identity proof.</p>
                            <p>
                                <b>Delivery Location:</b></p>
                            <p>
                                Orders can be delivered to only Residential, Commercial Location or can be 
                                delivered to any nearby Malabar Gold and Diamonds Showroom in India. The 
                                delivery of the orders cannot be done to any public places like Mall, Hotel, 
                                Restaurant, Hostel, On Road etc.</p>
                            <p>
                                If at all the recipient is unavailable during the time of delivery, Courier 
                                Company will try make 3 attempts to deliver the product. In case you are still 
                                not reachable/ available, the same will be returned to our office from where the 
                                product has been dispatched (Mumbai).</p>
                            <p>
                                <b>Change in Shipping Address:</b></p>
                            <p>
                                - Customer can check the status &amp; track their orders by log-in into their 
                                Malabar Account.</p>
                            <p>
                                - Change of Shipping details can also be done at customer’s end. Once the order 
                                is created, customer can change shipping address only till the order is actually 
                                shipped from our facility. If customer wants to change shipping address, they 
                                should log in into their respective account and click on &quot;Change Shipping 
                                Address&quot; button, which is next to shipping address and then change the address. 
                                Such icon will be active till order status is changed to “Shipped”. Once this is 
                                done, the link that states &quot;Change Shipping Address&quot; will get inactive.</p>
                            <p>
                                Guarantee of the delivery of the product is subject to the terms and conditions 
                                of courier company. Any kind of discrepancy in the details of the receiver will 
                                result in non-delivery of such product.</p>
                            <p>
